snippet.title: BLUNT FORCE 🌹 VR | Game Teaser
snippet.description:
🌹 Peace and war, spy and soldier, riddles and combats. All is blurred and banded together in time. Who are you? What is happening? Fulfill your duty and unravel the mystery in Blunt Force.
(more information below)

It's a teaser of Blunt Force, upcoming VR action game. Stay tuned:
👍 http://facebook.com/PlayBluntForce
🐦 http://twitter.com/PlayBluntForce
🎮 http://store.steampowered.com/app/816070

Developed by Monad Rock (www.monadrock.com)
